title: WSBTV News
description:
The WSB-TV News app brings you Atlanta-area news, weather, sports, traffic, and more. The app has been completely redesigned to ease of use and a more pleasing experience. For instance, we’ve made it easier for you to find live streaming video so you can watch our newscasts and/or breaking news coverage as it happens. We also gave you quick access to weather, traffic and the top local headlines. We strive to provide you with the best in local news and info, so check out our app and watch for updates as we make it even better.
Please note: This app features Nielsen’s proprietary measurement software which will allow you to contribute to market research, like Nielsen’s TV Ratings. Please see www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.
